iDAW - Intelligent Digital Audio Workstation
=============================================

Version: 1.0.0
Codename: Dual Engine
Build Date: 2025
Platform: macOS 10.15+ / Windows 10+ / Linux

Components:
-----------
- Music Brain (Python AI Engine): 1.0.0
- iDAW Core (C++ Audio Engine): 1.0.0
- Orchestrator: 1.0.0
- Bridge API: 1.0.0

Plugins:
--------
- Plugin 001: The Eraser (Spectral Gating) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 002: The Pencil (Tube Saturation) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 003: The Press (VCA Compressor) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 004: The Smudge (Convolution Reverb) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 005: The Trace (Delay) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 006: The Palette (Wavetable Synth) - 1.0.0
- Plugin 007: The Parrot (Vocal/Instrument Companion) - 1.0.0

Architecture:
-------------
- Dual Heap Memory: Side A (4GB RT-Safe) + Side B (Dynamic AI/UI)
- Python Bridge: pybind11 embedded interpreter
- Shaders: OpenGL 3.3+ (Da Vinci Protocol)
- Ghost Hands: AI-driven parameter automation

